              </div>
            </div>
            <h2 class="text-headline text-white mb-5" style="white-space: pre-line;">Your page, built&#10;for every visitor.</h2>
            <p class="text-body-lg text-zinc-400 mb-8 leading-relaxed">PelloPitch reads the visitor — their source, industry, and intent — and builds a unique landing page for them in real time. The headline changes. The offer shifts. The copy speaks directly to them. No templates. No A/B tests. Just pages that convert.</p>
            <ul class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-10 list-none m-0 p-0" role="list">
              <li class="feature-pill" style="background: #d946ef0d; color: #d946ef; border-color: #d946ef25;"><svg width="10" height="10" viewBox="0 0 10 10" fill="none"><path d="M2 5l2.5 2.5L8 2.5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>Real-time page generation</li>
              <li class="feature-pill" style="background: #d946ef0d; color: #d946ef; border-color: #d946ef25;"><svg width="10" height="10" viewBox="0 0 10 10" fill="none"><path d="M2 5l2.5 2.5L8 2.5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>Per-visitor personalisation</li>
              <li class="feature-pill" style="background: #d946ef0d; color: #d946ef; border-color: #d946ef25;"><svg width="10" height="10" viewBox="0 0 10 10" fill="none"><path d="M2 5l2.5 2.5L8 2.5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>Source &amp; intent detection</li>
              <li class="feature-pill" style="background: #d946ef0d; color: #d946ef; border-color: #d946ef25;"><svg width="10" height="10" viewBox="0 0 10 10" fill="none"><path d="M2 5l2.5 2.5L8 2.5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>8–12% conversion rates</li>
            </ul>
            <a href="https://pellopitch.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn-primary self-start" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #d946ef 0%, #d946efcc 100%);">
              Explore PelloPitch
