              <li class="feature-pill" style="background: #d946ef0d; color: #d946ef; border-color: #d946ef25;"><svg width="10" height="10" viewBox="0 0 10 10" fill="none"><path d="M2 5l2.5 2.5L8 2.5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>8–12% conversion rates</li>
